rking on PLing a warrior for guild needs.  The warrior I am working on is wearing Kunark era equipment.  I don't claim to know anything about warriors, I'm a bst at heart.  What I'm needing to know is:<br>
<br>
what is a realistic hp / ac to aim for in the mid to late 50's<br>
<br>
what equipment can I get him to satisfy those numbers while keeping it relatively cheap or farming with a group or two.  Keep in mind that I need to do it fast.  I have about 8 days to get him up to snuff in levels and equipment.<br>
<br>
what high aggro weapons can I look for?  Don't need DPS at this point, our melee is sufficient in that area.<br>
<br>
He is 52 now, and I need to get him up and ready for HoT.  We can finish what we don't get there in the way of armor, but I got to make sure he survives the first few nights.<br>
<br>
